A ghost squad officer has come under fire for allegedly dragging a motorist out of his car, pepper-spraying him and keeping him in a choke hold, which can be seen in a video that has gone viral. The motorist allegedly suffered a dislocated shoulder.    Video: FACEBOOK The officer is also heard threatening the person recording the incident. However, the officer denies the version of events posted on social media, and says the driver was pulled over for reckless and negligent driving, and for disregarding a lawful instruction to pull over and attempted to flee the scene.